                          <span class="text"> <TABLE WIDTH="100%" CELLPADDING=5 BORDER=0><TR><TD VALIGN="TOP" COLSPAN=2><SPAN CLASS="header">Rating </SPAN><IMG SRC="/stccg/global/images/rating/9.gif" BORDER=0></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN="TOP"><A HREF="deckread.php3?deck=82"><IMG SRC="/stccg/global/images/read.gif" BORDER=0></A></TD><TD><A HREF="deckreview.php3?deck=82"><IMG SRC="/stccg/global/images/review.gif" BORDER=0></A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><span class=header>Author</Span></TD><TD><span class=text><A HREF="../membercenter/directory/memberpage.php3?member=5763">Joshua "Capt Barclay" Carey</A></span></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN="TOP"><SPAN CLASS="header">Date Transmitted</SPAN></TD><TD WIDTH="90%"><span class=text>March 24, 2001</span></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN="TOP"><SPAN CLASS="header">Description</SPAN></TD><TD WIDTH="90%" ><span class=text>A purely fun deck revolving around the number 42. With this deck, whenever something 42-related happens, you are to say 42, the goal being to win the game with 100 points as much as saying 42 at least 42 times.</span></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN="TOP"><SPAN CLASS="header">Card List</SPAN></TD><TD WIDTH="90%" ><span class=text><TABLE WIDTH="100%" CELLPADDING=5 BORDER=0><TR><TD VALIGN="TOP"><span class=text>Seed Deck (30- 42 if free seeds and side deck cards counted)<br>
